<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .failure-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .failure-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .button-group {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .button-group a {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="failure-container">
        <div class="failure-icon">‚ùå</div>
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        <p class="message">
            Unfortunately, your NETS payment could not be completed.
            <br>
            Please try again or use a different payment method.
        </p>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <strong>What you can do:</strong>
            <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Try scanning the QR code again</li>
                <li>Check your bank app for any issues</li>
                <li>Use a different payment method</li>
                <li>Contact support if the issue persists</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/payment" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg">
                Try Again
            </a>
            <a href="/shopping" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">
                Back to Shopping
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
